    Function reference

    All functions

    achilles()
    Runs ACHILLES on AmsterdamUMCdb converted to the OMOP CDM
    alter_system_settings()
    Alters PostgreSQL System settings.
    cloud_auth()
    Small wrapper for authentication https://github.com/ropensci/googleLanguageR. Allows authentication using Google Cloud API credentials in default user folder'
    connect()
    Connect to database
    create_cdm_indices()
    Create Indices on Common Data Model Tables.
    create_cdm_tables()
    Create Common Data Model tables
    create_cohort_tables()
    Create the Common Data Model Results Cohort Tables
    create_config()
    Creates amstel configuration file
    create_data_tables()
    Create the Common Data Model Clinical Data tables
    create_environment()
    Creates a new database environment (database schemes) for AmsterdamUMCdb and the CDM data and results schemes for testing and/or example purposes.
    create_vocabulary_tables()
    Create the Common Data Model Vocabulary tables
    create_webapi_tables()
    Create OHDSI WebAPI tables
    data_quality_dashboard()
    Shows the OHDSI Data Quality Dashboard with the most recents results
    download_drivers()
    Downloads JDBC drivers
    drop_data_tables()
    Drop CDM Data Tables.
    drop_vocabulary_tables()
    Drop Vocabulary Tables.
    etl()
    Runs the main ETL steps for converting AmsterdamUMCdb to the OMOP CDM
    execute_dqd_checks()
    Evaluate Data Quality of AmsterdamUMCdb OMOP CDM after ETL.
    extract_concepts()
    Extract concepts
    get_config()
    Gets the configuration for working with the amstel package. Reads the config.yaml file from the user config folder or creates a new file if the configuration file is missing.
    get_server_tablename()
    Get case-sensitive table name on server
    has_adb_environment()
    Checks whether the AmsterdamUMCdb environment is available for running example code
    has_cdm_environment()
    Checks whether the CDM environment is available for running example code
    has_example_environment()
    Checks whether an example environment can be used
    index_data_tables()
    Create Indices on Common Data Model clinical data tables.
    index_vocabulary_tables()
    Create Indices on Common Data Model vocabulary tables.
    load_concepts()
    Load concepts
    load_data_tables()
    Load CDM Standardized Clinical Data Tables.
    load_source_to_concept_map()
    Load source_to_concept_map table from Usagi mapping Files.
    load_usagi_concepts()
    Load Usagi Concepts
    load_vocabulary_tables()
    Load Vocabulary Tables From CSV Files.
    read_vocabulary()
    Read vocabulary
    save_concepts()
    Save Concepts
    show_dqd_log()
    Show Data Quality Dashboard log (Shiny App)
    swap_usagi_counts()
    Swap counts
    translate()
    Small wrapper for translating using googleLanguageR.
    translate_concepts()
    Translate concepts
